    "description": {
      "value": "\n                <i>You can take advantage of your opponent's confusion, delivering multiple blows.</i>\n                <br />\n                <br />\n                \n                <p><b>Prerequisites</b></p>\n                <p> Improved Unarmed Strike, Gorgon's Fist, Scorpion Style, base attack bonus +11.</p>\n                \n            <br />\n                <p><b>Benefits</b></p>\n                <p><p class=\"stat-block-1\"> Whenever you use the full-attack action and make at least one unarmed strike, you can make two additional unarmed strikes at your highest base attack bonus. These bonus attacks must be made against a dazed, flat-footed, paralyzed, staggered, stunned, or unconscious foe.</p></p>\n                \n            \n            "
